data.name: Label3.Text
data.value: The Golfer's Log allows users to enter their unique golfer ID, First Name and Last Name. It allows users choose their favorite major and minor PGA tournament. The log also allows players to enter in their handicap and average score. If your handicap is registered with the USGA check the "Yes" box. The log also keeps track of the last time the golfer has played and what his or her favorite time of day is to play. Lastly, it allows the user to enter his or her favorite golfer.
